title: Poll: 0% of Black Voters Say They Had a Poor Experience Voting in Georgia
description: No black voters had a poor experience voting in the 2022 midterm elections in Georgia, according to a poll conducted by the University of Georgia.
author: Ashley Oliver, Ashley Oliver

title: Poll: Trump Towers over Potential GOP Primary Opponents with 35-Point Lead
description: Former President Donald Trump holds a whopping 35-point lead over the rest of the potential 2024 Republican primary field, according to a poll.
author: Nick Gilbertson, Nick Gilbertson

title: Stacey Abrams adviser said burning police car, smashing windows isn't 'violence' after anti-cop chaos
description: A top adviser at a Stacey Abrams-founded nonprofit defended Atlanta anti-cop rioters, saying burning a police car and smashing windows is not 'violence.'
author: Joe Schoffstall | Fox News

title: Poll shows 0% of Black voters had 'poor' voting experience in November despite Biden claim of 'Jim Crow 2.0'
description: A new poll in Georgia shows that 0% of Black voters thought their voting experience was "poor" despite a newly enacted law that Democrats claimed was "Jim Crow 2.0."
author: Andrew Mark Miller | Fox News
